spec_data.Name: rubygem-multi_test
spec_data.Description:
multi_test gives a uniform interface onto whatever testing library has been
loaded into a running Ruby process. It can be used to clobber autorun behaviour
from older versions of Test::Unit that automatically hook in when the user
requires them.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 04:47:43 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Wafter-thin gem to disable autorun of various testing libraries
